Package edu.internet2.middleware.grouperInstallerExt.org.apache.commons.compress.compressors.xz Description

Provides stream classes for compressing and decompressing streams using the XZ algorithm.

The classes in this package are wrappers around edu.internet2.middleware.grouperInstallerExt.org.tukaani.xz.XZInputStream and edu.internet2.middleware.grouperInstallerExt.org.tukaani.xz.XZOutputStream provided by the public domain XZ for Java library.
